originalText.text:
Working with Janet at Empire Professional Workforce Solutions to secure my current position has been a dream in so many ways. It is truly an understatement to say that she is the golden standard for all recruiters. I wish for everybody to work with somebody like Janet during their job search.

Since the very beginning, Janet has demonstrated such a genuine care for candidates and has an eye for what employers are looking for. She touched base very frequently to make sure that I was kept up to date about the status of my application, that I was feeling good and prepared with the material I was submitting, and that I was confident in myself going forward.

She always went above and beyond in all stages of the application process. She took as much time as was needed to answer any and all questions, talk me through what the application process would consist of, what qualities the employer is looking for, and how to best exhibit all of my experience to prospective employers. Janet is incredibly kind, sharp, and holds herself and job applicants to high standards in order to get them to put their best foot forward.

For a fresh college graduate like me, Janet’s wit, dedication, timeliness, and persistence helped me to ease into the intimidating realms of job hunting and full-time work. Because of all that Janet has taught me through her guidance and our conversations during my application process, I had the most ideal entrance into the workplace and am forever grateful for her.

originalText.text:
Working with Janet was unlike working with any other recruiter. Most recruiters I've dealt with clearly couldn't care less, were low energy, and were poor communicators.

Janet cared about me. A lot.

I worked with her over a couple months to get me my first job out of college. There was a pre-screening stage, as well as two back-to-back interviews. Janet walked me through every step of the process and helped me tailor my resume and interview answers. Even after I got the job, Janet called me to help me understand the benefits package. She was also quite supportive. I don't think I've ever met someone so determined to help me in my life. She used my other second stage interviews to get my current employer to push up their timeline. She also pulled my references and provided their testimonials to my employer for me.

I'm incredibly grateful for my experience with Empire Workforce Solutions.

originalText.text: I worked with Janet to get my current job after I graduated. She was so incredibly helpful communicating everything that was expected with the role and updating me with any information throughout the process. Really picked a great role with a law firm that fit me perfectly.  I’ve worked with 2 other employment  agencies and I can say this was one of the best, they are not just trying to fill roles to check off a box but instead of making sure you and the company/role are a good fit.

originalText.text: It was an absolute pleasure working with Empire to find a role that would fit my skillset and experience level. Anthony and Michael had actually reached out to me after applying to a different role on Indeed. Upon our initial conversation, the folks at Empire were able to find a different role which turned out to be a perfect fit for me. Empire's staff conducted the recruiting process with outstanding levels of professionalism and consideration. 2 years later and counting, I could not be happier with the role and company Empire placed me with.
